    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's come inside-- policemen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I hear what they shot-- shots more because the barn was near to the highway where the truck was standing in what we take.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The policeman comes with the owner from the-- I think what this was the owner.",
