    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know where-- if I got something inside, where it was, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I know he will come now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He will shot me, or kill me, or what he will do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my luck, when he comes on the top, Understand that he take the straw from one side the other side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He take from the middle and begin to pull them in one side and the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he put on me maybe a couple more straw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hear what he said, where he-- where he can be?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's not here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, something's [BACKGROUND NOISE] easier on my heart become and he come down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, I stay-- and it was maybe from the police where they shot all the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, maybe a quarter mile, less than a quarter mile.",
